sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (client)
    participant API as API
    participant UserClass as User (Model)
    participant DB as Storage (FileStorage/DB)

    U->>+API: POST /api/v1/users { first_name, last_name, email, password }
    API->>+UserClass: User(first_name, last_name, email, password)
    UserClass->>UserClass: inherits BaseModel.__init__()
    UserClass->>+DB: save()
    DB-->>-UserClass: confirm stored
    UserClass-->>-API: to_dict()
    API-->>-U: 201 Created { id, first_name, last_name, email }

    Note over UserClass: password stored as -String (private)<br>id/created_at/updated_at from BaseModel
